{"product_id":"the-lifespan-of-love-frankenstein-art-poster-movie-poster","title":"The Lifespan of Love | Frankenstein Art Poster | Movie Poster","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"703\" data-end=\"1014\"\u003eCelebrate one of the most tender reinterpretations of classic literature with this beautifully illustrated \u003cstrong data-start=\"810\" data-end=\"846\"\u003eFrankenstein Romantic Art Poster\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003cbr data-start=\"847\" data-end=\"850\"\u003eThe artwork captures a quiet, intimate moment between Elizabeth and the Creature — a scene painted with emotion, vulnerability, and the aching beauty of connection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1016\" data-end=\"1400\"\u003eWrapped in flowing white fabric and soft painterly textures, Elizabeth rests gently against the Creature, while a single autumn leaf glows like a symbol of hope in his hand.\u003cbr data-start=\"1189\" data-end=\"1192\"\u003eThe quote,\u003cbr data-start=\"1202\" data-end=\"1205\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1205\" data-end=\"1268\"\u003e“To be lost and to be found, that is the lifespan of love.”\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr data-start=\"1268\" data-end=\"1271\"\u003eadds a poetic depth, turning this illustration into a visual meditation on longing, acceptance, and the redemptive power of love.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1402\" data-end=\"1583\"\u003eThe contrasting color palette — warm red on one side, cool blue on the other — enhances the duality of their worlds: fear and comfort, despair and tenderness, creation and humanity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1585\" data-end=\"1720\"\u003ePerfect for bedrooms, reading corners, art studios, libraries, or anyone who loves emotional storytelling and atmospheric illustration.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1722\" data-end=\"1801\"\u003eThis poster is not just décor — it’s a moment of love captured in brushstrokes.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51290320503080,"sk